{"type":"article_comment","id":499969,"parentType":"article","parentId":24254,"uid":56544,"contents":"裁判，那有人球踢了又踢踢了又踢踢了又踢<br>\n那只好剪了又貼剪了又貼剪了又貼<br>\n<br>\n湖南人<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTYlOUIlQkUlRTklOUQlOUM\">曾靜</a>在閱讀呂留良的<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTglOTElOTclRTQlQkQlOUM\">著作</a>之後大受激勵，在雍正六年（1728年）派遣門徒<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlQkMlQTAlRTclODYlOTk\">張熙</a>遊說川陝總督<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlQjIlQjMlRTklOTIlOUYlRTclOTAlQUE\">岳鍾琪</a>反清，被告發下獄，釀成了轟動一時的呂留良案。<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTklOUIlOEQlRTYlQUQlQTMlRTUlQjglOUQ\">雍正帝</a>親著作《<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlQTQlQTclRTclQkUlQTklRTglQTYlQkElRTglQkYlQjclRTklOEMlODQ\">大義覺迷錄</a>》一書頒行全國，親自解說駁斥呂留良的言論。<br>\n岳鍾琪汗<br>\n乾隆十三年（1748年）三月，由於<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlQTQlQTclRTUlQjAlOEYlRTklODclOTElRTUlQjclOUQlRTQlQjklOEIlRTUlQkQlQjk\">大金川叛亂</a>而清廷出兵多時未果，<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTQlQjklQkUlRTklOUElODYlRTUlQjglOUQ\">乾隆帝</a>想到岳鍾琪，決意重召，先授予他<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTclQjglQkQlRTUlODUlQjU\">總兵</a>之銜，後改授<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlOUIlOUIlRTUlQjclOUQ\">四川</a><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTYlOEYlOTAlRTclOUQlQTM\">提督</a>，賜孔雀花翎，乾隆十四年正月，岳鍾琪隨<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTclQjYlOTMlRTclOTUlQTUlRTUlQUUlODklRTYlOTIlQUIlRTQlQkQlQkY\">經略</a><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlQTQlQTclRTUlQUQlQjglRTUlQTMlQUI\">大學士</a><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlODIlODUlRTYlODElOTI\">傅恆</a>參與平定大金川<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlOUMlOUYlRTUlOEYlQjg\">土司</a>叛亂之戰，連續攻占康八達、塔高等山頭，之後長驅直入，莎羅奔勒烏圍（今四川<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTklODclOTElRTUlQjclOUQlRTUlOEUlQkY\">金川縣</a>東）大營，叛亂<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTklODUlOEIlRTklOTUlQjc\">酋長</a><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvdy9pbmRleC5waHA_dGl0bGU9JUU4JThFJThFJUU3JUJFJTg1JmFjdGlvbj1lZGl0JnJlZGxpbms9MQ\">莎羅</a>以前跟隨過岳鍾琪平西藏，討青海，因而懼於岳鍾琪，只好乞降。投降後，清廷保持其<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlOUMlOUYlRTUlOEYlQjg\">土司</a>的任命。三月，恢復爵位，後子孫降等世襲。<br>\n乾隆十五年（1750年），<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTglQTUlQkYlRTglOTclOEY\">西藏</a><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTclOEYlQTAlRTclODglQkUlRTklQkIlOTglRTclODklQjklRTklODIlQTMlRTYlOUMlQTglRTYlOUMlQUQlRTUlOEIlOTI\">珠爾默特那木札勒</a>叛亂，時年64歲的岳鍾琪奉命出兵<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTUlQkElQjclRTUlQUUlOUElRTUlQjglODI\">康定</a>，會同總督<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTclQUQlOTYlRTYlQTUlOUU\">策楞</a>，結果成功討平叛亂。乾隆十九年（1754年），岳鍾琪抱重病出征鎮壓<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvdy9pbmRleC5waHA_dGl0bGU9JUU5JTk5JUIzJUU3JTkwJUE4JmFjdGlvbj1lZGl0JnJlZGxpbms9MQ\">陳琨</a>時，病卒四川資州（今四川<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTglQjUlODQlRTQlQjglQUQ\">資中</a>），時年六十八歲，<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC5tLndpa2lwZWRpYS5vcmcvd2lraS8lRTQlQjklQkUlRTklOUElODYlRTUlQjglOUQ\">乾隆帝</a>賜諡「襄勤」。<br>\n沒招了嗎？換換<br>\n現在已經練就看id辨是非","date":"2020-09-20","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}